# Stored Procedures Design
- lowercase, underscores 
- begin with entity  
- clear domain prefix (e.g. `user_`, `report_`, `organization_`)  
- descriptive action verbs (`create`, `update`, `delete`, `set`, `add`, `activate`, etc.)  
- append `_v2`, `_v3` for breaking changes  
- no vague names like `do_stuff` or `process`

